[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0488","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0488.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0294","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 WINS SNMP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的 WINS 数据库通过 SNMP 协议可被远程攻击者删除所有记录，导致拒绝服务。攻击者无需认证即可通过 SNMP 发送恶意请求，删除 WINS 服务中的所有 NetBIOS 名称记录，造成网络名称解析服务瘫痪。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0294"],"sources":["cve","avd","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"1999-01-01","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全更新或禁用不必要的 SNMP 服务，限制 SNMP 访问权限，配置 SNMP 社区字符串为强密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0294","https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0294","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0294"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0488.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0472","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0472.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0283","title":"Sun Java Web Server 源代码泄露漏洞","description":"Sun Java Web Server 1.1 Beta 存在源代码泄露漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过直接请求 .jhtml 文件获取其原始源代码。该漏洞源于服务器对 .jhtml 文件的处理逻辑缺陷，未能正确解析执行而直接返回文件内容，导致 CGI 程序的源代码、数据库连接信息及业务逻辑等敏感数据暴露。攻击者只需发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可利用，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0283"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 Sun Java Web Server 1.1 正式版或更高版本（如 2.0），该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，在服务器配置中将 .jhtml 文件映射至 Java Servlet 处理器而非静态文件处理器，并禁止目录遍历。鉴于该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至 Oracle iPlanet Web Server 或 Apache Tomcat 等现代替代方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88256790401004&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20375","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0283.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0283","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0283.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0283.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8q69-243x-44f9/GHSA-8q69-243x-44f9.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0283.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9ebd3145-ae01-469d-9fe2-ea9bfed3c14f.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0472.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0472.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0472.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0412","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0412.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0226","title":"Microsoft Windows NT IP 分片拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 系统的 TCP/IP 协议栈在实现 IP 分片重组逻辑时存在缺陷，未能正确处理经过分片（fragmentation）的 IP 数据包，导致内核在处理畸形分片时出现资源耗尽或崩溃。攻击者可构造并发送特制的 IP 分片包序列，在无需身份认证的情况下远程触发目标系统的拒绝服务（DoS）状态，使受影响的 Windows NT 主机蓝屏重启或停止响应网络请求。该漏洞影响运行 TCP/IP 服务的 Windows NT 系列系统，远程可达即可利用，可导致关键服务长时间不可用。微软后续通过安全补丁修复了分片重组处理逻辑。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0226"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4（SP4）或更高版本，该补丁已修复 TCP/IP 协议栈对分片 IP 数据包处理不当的问题。若无法立即安装补丁，应在边界防火墙或路由器上过滤并丢弃入站的分片 IP 数据包（Fragment Offset 大于 0 的报文），禁止将此类碎片转发至内网主机；如该主机不作路由器使用，可关闭注册表 EnableRouting/EnableProxy 以禁用 IP 转发；同时部署入侵检测规则拦截 Teardrop 类畸形分片攻击，并仅开放必要的网络端口以缩小攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0226"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0412.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0395","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0395.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0209","title":"SunOS 4.1.x SunView selection_svc 远程文件读取漏洞","description":"SunOS 4.1.x 系统自带的 SunView 图形环境提供的 selection_svc 服务存在未授权访问缺陷，远程攻击者无需认证即可连接该服务并读取目标主机上的任意文件内容。攻击条件为：目标主机运行 SunView 且开放 selection_svc 服务端口，攻击者处于可与其网络连通的位置。该漏洞可导致系统敏感信息（如口令文件、配置文件等）泄露，危害系统安全。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0209"],"sources":["exploitdb","cve"],"published":"1999-01-01","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"升级到已修复该问题的 SunOS 补丁版本，或禁用 SunView 的 selection_svc 服务并限制相关端口的网络访问，仅在受信任的内部网络中开放。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T08:26:46.410016186+00:00","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/195","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0209"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/195"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/195"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0395.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0371","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0371.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0188","title":"Sun Solaris passwd 命令拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统中的 passwd 命令存在拒绝服务漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 passwd 命令发送特制输入或触发异常状态，导致 passwd 进程崩溃或系统认证服务不可用，进而使得合法用户无法正常修改密码，影响系统正常运维。该漏洞影响多个 Solaris 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需具备本地访问权限，利用条件相对有限，但成功利用后可能导致系统认证功能瘫痪。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0188"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:47.230","remediation":"建议升级到已修复此漏洞的 Solaris 版本（如 Solaris 2.6 及以上补丁版本），或安装 Sun 提供的对应安全补丁。临时缓解措施可限制非授权用户对 passwd 命令的执行权限，或通过文件系统 ACL 控制 /usr/bin/passwd 的访问范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/182"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0371.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0290","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0290.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0139","title":"Sun Solaris x86 mkcookie 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris x86 系统中的 mkcookie 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该程序传递特製的参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖内存中的返回地址或函数指针，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris x86 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用此漏洞提权至 root。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0139"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:40.823","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方安全补丁 106980-01 (Solaris 2.5.1) 或 106981-01 (Solaris 2.6)。如无法打补丁，立即移除 `mkcookie` 的 setuid root 权限：`chmod 0555 /usr/bin/mkcookie`，或直接删除该程序。限制本地普通用户登录受影响系统作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/8205"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0290.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0718","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0718.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0463","title":"SGI IRIX fcagent 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 操作系统中的 fcagent 组件存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制请求，利用该组件在处理异常输入时的缺陷，导致系统服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。攻击无需身份认证即可远程触发，影响 SGI IRIX 6.4 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0463"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.940","remediation":"应用 SGI 安全公告 19981201-01-PX 提供的补丁程序修复 fcagent 组件。如无需使用该服务，建议停止 fcagent 运行（/etc/init.d/fcagent stop）并通过防火墙限制对相关端口的网络访问。SGI IRIX 6.4 已停止技术支持，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0463","https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0463"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0718.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0561","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0561.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0342","title":"Linux PAM 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux PAM（可插拔认证模块）存在不安全的临时文件创建漏洞，本地攻击者可通过在/tmp目录下创建符号链接指向目标文件，诱导使用了共享库的PAM模块在提升权限的过程中读写临时文件，从而利用条件竞争漏洞覆盖系统关键文件或执行任意代码，最终获取root权限。该漏洞影响多种Linux发行版及使用了PAM模块的UNIX类系统，攻击者需具备本地账户访问权限，CVSS评分6.2，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0342"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.490","remediation":"建议升级 Linux PAM 至 0.64 及以上版本，该版本已修复临时文件竞争条件漏洞，改用 mkstemp() 安全创建临时文件。旧版 Red Hat Linux 用户应安装 RHSA-1999:013 公告对应补丁。如无法升级，可限制不可信用户的本地登录权限，并启用严格的 umask 策略作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0342"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0561.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0548","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0548.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0332","title":"Microsoft NetMeeting 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"NetMeeting 中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的恶意数据包触发该漏洞，导致目标程序拒绝服务甚至远程命令执行。该漏洞影响早期 Windows 系统中捆绑的 NetMeeting 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0332"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.323","remediation":"安装微软 KB Q184346 官方安全补丁。由于 NetMeeting 已被微软停止支持并从现代 Windows 中移除，建议通过控制面板卸载 NetMeeting 组件，或升级到不再包含 NetMeeting 的 Windows 版本。如暂时无法卸载，可在防火墙层面阻止 TCP 端口 1720（H.323）、1503 和 1731 以限制 NetMeeting 的网络访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ184346","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0332.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0332","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0332.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0332.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5783344e7c4adc3f449b78e346f760d75b095a9c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v76w-cp5w-h37c/GHSA-v76w-cp5w-h37c.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0332.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ffe2b56c-4de2-4b2f-a439-b4918b02fb5a.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0548.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0727","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0727.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0478","title":"HP-UX Sendmail 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sendmail 在处理连接请求时存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向运行 Sendmail 8.8.6 的 HP-UX 系统发送大量恶意连接请求，导致邮件服务耗尽系统资源而崩溃或无法响应正常请求。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 平台，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等，无需认证即可远程触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0478"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-12-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.3 或更高版本。如无法升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中设置 MaxDaemonChildren 和 ConnectionRateThrottle 参数限制并发连接数以缓解拒绝服务攻击。具体补丁信息参见 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9904-097。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0478","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9904-097"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0727.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0533","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0533.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0321","title":"Sun Solaris kcms_configure 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.5.1 系统中的 kcms_configure 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于未对用户输入进行充分边界检查，本地攻击者可通过向该命令传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存数据并执行任意代码以获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.5.1 操作系统，需要本地用户权限方可利用，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0321"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-12-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Solaris 至 2.6 及以上版本，或安装 Sun 安全补丁 105401-01 (SPARC) / 105402-01 (x86)。如无法升级，移除 kcms_configure 的 setuid 位：chmod 0755 /usr/openwin/bin/kcms_configure 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0321","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19342","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/928db9679b69032a137f1c2f3374c28367145ef0/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0321.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0321","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0321.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0321.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j357-gv2q-h95j/GHSA-j357-gv2q-h95j.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0321.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0533.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0148","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0148.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0057","title":"FreeBSD vacation 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统自带的 vacation 自动回复程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制的电子邮件，触发 vacation 程序在自动回复时通过 sendmail 命令执行任意系统命令。该漏洞允许未经身份认证的远程攻击者在受影响系统上以邮件用户权限执行命令，危害等级高，CVSS 评分 7.5。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0057"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-11-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.587","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 3.2-RELEASE 或更高版本，该版本已修复 vacation 程序命令注入漏洞。如在受影响的 FreeBSD 3.x/4.0 系统上无法升级，可移除或禁用 vacation setuid 位（`chmod 755 /usr/bin/vacation`）并限制 sendmail 对 .forward 文件中 vacation 管道的调用权限。若业务上无需自动回复功能，直接卸载 vacation（`pkg_delete vacation`）或注释 .forward 中的 vacation 调用作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9811-087"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0148.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0141","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0141.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0052","title":"FreeBSD/OpenBSD IP碎片重组空指针解引用拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 和 OpenBSD 操作系统在处理 IP 分片重组时存在空指针解引用漏洞 (CWE-476)。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送精心构造的异常 IP 分片数据包，当内核试图对这些分片进行重组时会因空指针解引用导致系统崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 1.x/2.x、OpenBSD 2.2/2.3 及 BSD/OS 4.0 等多个版本，CVSS v3.1 评分 7.5，危害等级高。由于攻击无需任何特权且可远程触发，是早期 BSD 系统中影响广泛的拒绝服务漏洞之一。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0052"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:27.813","remediation":"建议升级 FreeBSD 至 2.2.8 及以上版本，或 OpenBSD 至 2.4 及以上版本；在防火墙层面丢弃入站分片数据包（如 iptables -A INPUT -f -j DROP），或在内核中禁用 IP 分片重组功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/908","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1389"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0141.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0439","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0439.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0254","title":"HP OpenView SNMP 团体字符串信息泄露漏洞","description":"HP OpenView 存在隐藏的 SNMP 团体字符串漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可利用该默认团体字符串访问 SNMP 服务，进而读取或修改 MIB 表中的敏感配置信息，导致信息泄露或设备配置被篡改。受影响的系统包括 HP OpenView 网络管理软件，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0254"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-11-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.633","remediation":"升级 HP OpenView 至 NNM 7.53 或更高版本以修复此已知漏洞；立即修改所有 SNMP 团体字符串，禁止使用默认的 public/private 及已知隐藏字符串；在防火墙上限制仅允许受信任的管理主机访问 UDP 161 端口；如业务不需要 SNMP 功能，建议直接禁用 OpenView 的 SNMP 代理服务以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0254","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-239","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-239/","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0254.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0254","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0254.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0254.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0254.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/c8b30957414aefbd6ba0b766db0d40593ba36fba/references/CVE-1999-0254-2025-03-17-1422","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p4hh-f88r-4p2r/GHSA-p4hh-f88r-4p2r.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest/blob/edcc863fa08f9024b1a3afc6f793747fed5f08ff/references/contrib1-CVE-1999-0254-2025-03-17-1422","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/snmp_default_communities.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0439.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0261","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0261.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0118","title":"IBM AIX 4.3 infod 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.3 系统的 infod 组件存在本地权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过 X display 机制向 infod 服务发送特制请求，利用该漏洞获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.3 版本系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用，成功利用后完全控制系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0118"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-11-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.630","remediation":"建议升级到 IBM AIX 4.3.3 及以上受支持版本，或安装对应 APAR 补丁 IX72357。如无需 infod 服务，可执行 `stopsrc -t infod` 停止该服务并通过注释 `/etc/inetd.conf` 中相关行禁用，以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91158980826979&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19287","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0118","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0118.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7pq8-h83c-wwjc/GHSA-7pq8-h83c-wwjc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0118.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6c29fe92-c11f-40b7-bc14-92d730f9e4fc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"r